%% Use case diagram: View Todos
flowchart LR
  user((User))
  ui[Web UI]
  api[GET /todos]
  repo[(SQLite DB)]

  user -->|opens app| ui
  ui -->|fetch on load| api
  api -->|SELECT ORDER BY created_at| repo
  repo -->|rows| api
  api -->|200 todo array| ui
  ui -->|renders list with completion status| user
